To your credit, your location
was well chosen.

45:03.455 --> 45:08.668
lt just needed a little cleaning,
a few lights, proper tools, of course.

45:09.920 --> 45:12.004
- l did it because of you.
- No.

45:13.757 --> 45:17.301
- You attacked them because you wanted to.
- But you inspired me.

45:17.428 --> 45:19.178
- l didn't.
- With your principles.

45:19.304 --> 45:21.347
- They're not my principles.
- They are.

45:21.473 --> 45:23.474
Don't tell me who l am.

45:24.685 --> 45:28.688
All my life, l've done what someone else said l
should. been who he said l should be.

45:28.814 --> 45:31.107
l followed his rules, stuck to his plan.

45:31.233 --> 45:35.319
l never stopped to think about what l wanted
and what l needed.

45:35.446 --> 45:38.364
And now l don't know
who l'm supposed to be.

45:39.158 --> 45:42.744
l'll tell you one thing, though.
l'm not the Bay Harbor Butcher.

45:43.746 --> 45:45.538
l'm not anybody's role model.

45:45.664 --> 45:48.541
What are you talking about, then?
Who are you?

45:48.667 --> 45:52.795
l'll let you know when l figure that out.
Though. l gotta tell you.

45:52.921 --> 45:58.634
l am well on my way. because. as sure
as l'm standing here, l don't need to kill you.

45:58.761 --> 46:01.763
- That's a relief.
- That need from within

46:01.889 --> 46:04.307
that always drives me to this table,

46:04.850 --> 46:06.809
l don't feel it.

46:10.147 --> 46:13.608
- l'm in recovery.
- Well, l knew you weren't gonna kill me.

46:13.734 --> 46:17.779
No, l'm gonna kill you. l have to.
l just don't need to.

46:17.905 --> 46:20.072
lt's very empowering.

46:46.767 --> 46:49.268
Anyone in there, make yourself known!

47:01.448 --> 47:04.200
- Arm.
- Leg.

47:04.910 --> 47:06.786
Head.

47:07.996 --> 47:10.206
lt's Olson, gift-wrapped.

47:10.332 --> 47:14.752
lt would seem the Butcher is watching us,
tracking the investigation.

47:14.878 --> 47:18.923
That wouldn't be too hard.
But why leave the body for us? That's a first.

47:19.049 --> 47:22.802
Probably didn't take too kindly
to the idea of Olson imitating him.

47:22.928 --> 47:25.096
lt's a pretty way to discourage others.

47:25.222 --> 47:28.266
l hate to say it but he probably
did us a favor.

47:28.392 --> 47:32.103
Take the law into your own hands.
the Bay Harbor boogeyman'll get you.

47:32.229 --> 47:36.524
lt's the first time we've been where
the Bay Harbor Butcher's actually been.

47:36.650 --> 47:38.734
Let's get busy.

47:44.825 --> 47:47.493
- Anybody seen Lundy?
- Over there on the phone.

47:47.619 --> 47:49.412
He's talking to DC, l think.

47:49.538 --> 47:52.164
Oh, shit. ls he gonna pull the case from us?

47:57.671 --> 48:00.506
Sure, have Robinson call me.
He's got my cell.

48:02.009 --> 48:04.385
l came over here for some privacy, Morgan.

48:04.511 --> 48:07.388
- sorry...
- Too much background noise over there.

48:07.514 --> 48:10.766
Hearing's the first thing to go.
Or is it memory? l always forget.

48:10.893 --> 48:14.437
You gonna pull the case from us?
You said if anybody died...

48:14.563 --> 48:17.440
At the hands of a vigilante.
This was our killer.

48:18.317 --> 48:23.070
l'm afraid you're still stuck with me.
Will your brother be here tomorrow?

48:23.864 --> 48:25.740
Yeah, l think so.

48:26.783 --> 48:29.410
l'll tell him you want him
in shouting distance.

48:29.536 --> 48:33.539
- Hey, what just happened?
- lt's cool.

48:33.665 --> 48:36.083
- He's always been the family superstar.
- Who?

48:36.209 --> 48:38.252
Dexter, your new go-to guy.

48:39.087 --> 48:43.215
Oh, this isn't about Dexter.
lt's about Masuka. l can't stand him.

48:43.342 --> 48:46.427
lf l hear one more titty joke,
l'll punch him in the face.

48:46.553 --> 48:48.721
Really?

48:50.724 --> 48:55.394
Any north unit,
request for escort from Orange Belt to JMS.

49:04.154 --> 49:06.030
Hey.

49:07.074 --> 49:08.991
Come on in.

49:09.576 --> 49:11.494
Sit down.

49:16.625 --> 49:19.168
l was angry before
when you tried to explain.

49:19.294 --> 49:21.420
This time l'll listen.

49:24.591 --> 49:27.468
l'm sorry l didn't tell you
about the road trip.

49:28.887 --> 49:30.763
Lila. . .

49:32.474 --> 49:35.726
came with me to Naples as my sponsor.

49:35.852 --> 49:39.605
- That's all.
- Why would you need her in Naples?

49:39.731 --> 49:42.108
You remember when l went out of town?

49:42.234 --> 49:44.902
l went to find the man who killed my mother.

49:45.028 --> 49:47.279
What are you talking about?

49:47.781 --> 49:52.702
A lot of stuff has been coming up for me in
recovery, things l never thought l'd deal with.

49:54.663 --> 49:58.499
l watched my mother die when l was three.

49:58.625 --> 50:00.501
Oh, Dexter.

50:02.754 --> 50:06.966
- l'm so sorry.
- She was murdered in front of me.

50:07.968 --> 50:09.927
l saw it happen.

50:11.638 --> 50:14.223
l think that has a lot to do
with why l'm...

50:17.602 --> 50:19.979
Why l do the things l do.

50:21.189 --> 50:23.399
Of course. Of course, it makes sense.

50:23.525 --> 50:27.194
l found the man who killed her in Naples.

50:27.320 --> 50:32.491
l thought maybe if l talked to him,
l could find some kind of closure.

50:34.161 --> 50:36.495
That's why Lila came with me, for support.

50:39.708 --> 50:44.462
- What?
- This was a huge moment in your life

50:45.714 --> 50:49.008
and you chose to include Lila but not me.

50:50.135 --> 50:52.845
- She's my sponsor.
- And l'm your girlfriend.

50:53.472 --> 50:56.265
l was afraid you wouldn't understand.

51:01.730 --> 51:03.481
OK.

51:05.108 --> 51:09.862
OK. So, let me try to understand now.

51:11.656 --> 51:14.325
You and Lila went away together

51:14.451 --> 51:17.078
as sponsor and sponsee.

51:19.164 --> 51:21.874
And you really did have adjoining rooms.

51:22.375 --> 51:24.126
Yes.

51:24.795 --> 51:27.588
- So, you didn't have sex that night?
- No.

51:29.674 --> 51:31.550
OK.

51:34.513 --> 51:36.514
Not that night.

51:41.436 --> 51:43.604
Leave.

51:43.730 --> 51:45.523
Rita.

51:46.566 --> 51:49.151
No, please. Leave now.

52:06.336 --> 52:09.880
There was a time I wouId have
done anything to protect Rita.

52:10.006 --> 52:13.592
I wouId have even Iied.
But today l told the truth

52:15.303 --> 52:17.304
even though l knew she'd get hurt.

52:27.440 --> 52:30.109
Maybe l am leaving the old me behind.
